record.title: DISPENSING WITH CALENDAR WEDNESDAY BUSINESS TODAY
record.narrative:
DISPENSING WITH CALENDAR WEDNESDAY BUSINESS TODAY -- (House of Representatives - December 10, 2008)

[Page: H10869]

speaking.paragraph: Madam Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that the business in order under the Calendar Wednesday rule be dispensed with today.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Washington?
